Hello bby!! I just want to thank you again kase nag effort ka talaga bumili jabee for our motmot! MWAAA ABABAYUUU! Apaka swerte ko talaga sayo! Mag 1 year na tayo pero jusq di man nabawasan pagmamahal, pag aaruga at iba pa mo saken. Nadagdagan lang lalo!! 

Naalala ko dati pag nag iinsecure/naaanxiety ako, lagi ko tinatanong sayo kung nabawasan ba pagmamahal mo saken ganun, tas paulit ulit. Tas ikaw naman sasabihin mo rin lagi paulit ulit na hindi nababawasan, madadagdagan lang lalo. And totoo nga! I never doubted you pero I'm just really happy to see na nadadagdagan lang nga lalo talaga pagmamahal mo saken. And I hope you feel the same bby! I hope na always mong maramdaman gaano nadadagdagan pagmamahal at pag aalaga ko sayo day by day. MWAAA MY BBY!!
